B.aUo=new A.bR("Share Certificate","Generate a visual certificate for a stock position to share.","Open a stock detail screen \u2192 tap Share Certificate.\n\nGenerates a stylised image showing:\n\u2022 Stock name and symbol\n\u2022 Number of shares held\n\u2022 Your average purchase price\n\u2022 Current value\n\nUseful for sharing investment milestones on social media.",null,B.a12)
